4.2 Fallback Version rights do not include access to new versions, updates, bug fixes, or new features released after
the Subscription Period expiry date.

4.3 Fallback Version rights are contingent on the Licensee having completed at least one full, paid Subscription
Period. Trial or complimentary activations do not qualify for Fallback Version rights.

4.4 All other terms of this Agreement, including restrictions in Section 5, continue to apply to use of the Fallback
Version.

